OL,6,FLike all professional players, Ashton
OL,7,FHewitt has a tough exterior.
OL,9,FThrough years of hard work and
OL,10,Fdedication, he has built a body that
OL,11,Fcan do things most cannot.
OL,13,FHe is a robust individual, built to
OL,14,Fwithstand enormous collisions. Built
OL,15,Fto run through brick walls.
OL,17,FBut everyone is fighting a battle
OL,18,Fnobody knows anything about and Hewitt
OL,19,Fis ready to talk about his.
