OL,6,FWe meet in the dressing room at Rodney
OL,7,FParade. It is a room he has sat in
OL,8,Fthousands of times.
OL,10,FIt's a room where Hewitt and his team-
OL,11,Fmates don their metaphorical armour
OL,12,Fbefore battle, mask any physical
OL,13,Fweaknesses with strapping and any
OL,14,Fmental vulnerabilities with silence.
OL,16,FBut now, during Mental Health
OL,17,FAwareness Week, it is time to talk.
OL,19,FOver his years growing up in , Hewitt
OL,20,Fexperienced in different forms.
