OL,11,FBut the modern world has brought a new
OL,12,Fvehicle for hate and it sits in the
OL,13,Fpalm of everyone's hand.
OL,15,FHewitt began using his platform on
OL,16,Fsocial media to raise awareness of
OL,17,Fsocial inequalities in society.
OL,19,FHe wanted to be a voice for change and
OL,20,Finstead he became a target.
