OL,3,C'It was overwhelming': rugby player on
OL,4,Cmental health impact of racist abuse
OL,6,FOn a daily basis, he would receive
OL,7,Ftorrents of abuse, usually from
OL,8,Fanonymous accounts. The nature of the
OL,9,Fvitriol being spewed into his mobile
OL,10,Fphone was harrowingly racist.
OL,12,FAs a result, his suffered.
OL,14,F"It was having a massive impact," he
OL,15,Ftold ITV Wales. "And it wasn't until
OL,16,Fmy partner told me that I needed to
OL,17,Fstop and take a step back because she
OL,18,Fcould notice that I wasn't being
OL,19,Fmyself. Losing my temper, just being
OL,20,Freally sensitive to things.
