OL,4,Cmental health impact of racist abuse
OL,6,F"I was a bit naive in thinking that I
OL,7,Fhad this mission to educate and, you
OL,8,Fknow, change the world and do my
OL,9,Flittle bit.
OL,11,F"I was trying to engage with
OL,12,Fabsolutely everybody who was trolling
OL,13,Fme or sending me abuse and making
OL,14,Fracist comments.
OL,16,F"I always just looked at it in the
OL,17,Fsense of for every 50 trolls, if I can
OL,18,Fchange someone's mind and change their
OL,19,Foutlook and their perspective and
OL,20,Feradicate racism in that one person,
OL,21,Fthen it would be worth it.
