OL,3,C'It was overwhelming': rugby player on
OL,4,Cmental health impact of racist abuse
OL,6,F"I just exhausted myself on the
OL,7,Fplatform, and it got to a point where
OL,8,Fit was just counterproductive and
OL,9,Ftaking its toll mentally on me. It got
OL,10,Ftoo much."
OL,12,FHewitt was attempting to reason with
OL,13,Faccounts who had no interest in
OL,14,Freasoned discussion.
OL,16,FAnd the weight of the abuse he
OL,17,Fexperienced began to impact those
OL,18,Faround him.
