OL,6,FThings rolled over into his
OL,7,Fprofessional life as a rugby player
OL,8,Ftoo. He admits that there were
OL,9,Foccasions he would be walking down the
OL,10,Ftunnel ready to enter the field in a
OL,11,Fpoor mental state.
OL,13,FSome of the abuse he'd receive would
OL,14,Frelate to his performance. Some hoped
OL,15,Fhe suffered a nasty injury.
OL,17,FHe'd ponder whether some of those who
OL,18,Fwere abusing him on social media were
OL,19,Fin the stands.
