OL,3,C'It was overwhelming': rugby player on
OL,4,Cmental health impact of racist abuse
OL,6,F"I didn't expect it to cross over and
OL,7,Ffor the trolls to start targeting my
OL,8,Fperformances on the pitch," he admits.
OL,10,F"As a professional athlete, you're
OL,11,Fused to criticism but I was receiving
OL,12,Fracial abuse directly related to
OL,13,Fwhatever game it was on the weekend.
OL,15,F"I'd end up sitting in the car after a
OL,16,Fgame, you know, not pulling off
OL,17,Fstraight away. I was on my phone
OL,18,Fthinking 'right, who has said what
OL,19,Fabout me? Who is being racist and what
OL,20,Fam I going to have to address?'
