OL,6,F"And then on the drive home, I'd be
OL,7,Fthinking 'right, how do I respond to
OL,8,Fthis?' And it was just consuming
OL,9,Feverything."
OL,11,FHewitt admits the rugby environment is
OL,12,Fnot an easy place to be vulnerable and
OL,13,Fto discuss any mental challenges you
OL,14,Fmight be dealing with.
