OL,6,FThere is a long way to go but,
OL,7,Fhappily, that situation is evolving
OL,8,Ffor the better. Hewitt is an
OL,9,Fambassador for charity Mind Cymru, who
OL,10,Fhave been invited by the Dragons to
OL,11,Fspeak to their players. He is
OL,12,Fchampioning more help for his peers in
OL,13,Fhis role as chair of the Welsh Rugby
OL,14,FPlayers' Association.
OL,16,FHewitt's experiences did make him
OL,17,Fquestion whether his efforts to
OL,18,Fhighlight discrimination and educate
OL,19,Fthe ignorant were worth it.
