OL,6,FFortunately, he has also enjoyed many
OL,7,Fpositive conversations and his tweets
OL,8,Fhave sparked further discussion and
OL,9,Feven real-world connections.
OL,11,FHe has been invited into to speak to
OL,12,Fchildren and received letters from
OL,13,Fyoungsters who "felt represented to
OL,14,Fsome extent, they could relate to the
OL,15,Fthings that I was saying".
OL,17,FBut there is more work to be done.
